<normalizedToken originalValue="à">a</normalizedToken>
Foligno&quot; []), Italy.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="30" pageNumber="31" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
The name often appears as &quot; 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pallary" authorityYear="1916" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis affinis" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="affinis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Melanopsis affinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Férussac”">Ferussac&quot;</normalizedToken>
in the literature (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation author="Wenz, W" journalOrPublisher="Gastropoda extramarina tertiaria" pageId="333" pageNumber="334" pagination="2503 - 2886" refId="B542" refString="Wenz, W, 1929. Fossilium Catalogus I: Animalia. Gastropoda extramarina tertiaria vol. IX: 2503 - 2886" title="Fossilium Catalogus I: Animalia." volume="vol. IX" year="1929">Wenz 1929</bibRefCitation>
: 2653; 
<bibRefCitation author="Esu, D" journalOrPublisher="Geologica Romana" pageId="307" pageNumber="308" pagination="203 - 294" publicationUrl="http://www.dst.uniroma1.it/geologicaromana/Volumi/VOL%2013/GR_13_203_293_Esu%20et%20al.pdf" refId="B136" refString="Esu, D, Girotti, O, 1975. La malacofauna continentale del Plio-Pleistocene dell'Italia centrale. I. Paleontologia. Geologica Romana 13: 203 - 294, http://www.dst.uniroma1.it/geologicaromana/Volumi/VOL%2013/GR_13_203_293_Esu%20et%20al.pdf" title="La malacofauna continentale del Plio-Pleistocene dell'Italia centrale. I. Paleontologia." url="http://www.dst.uniroma1.it/geologicaromana/Volumi/VOL%2013/GR_13_203_293_Esu%20et%20al.pdf" volume="13" year="1975">Esu and Girotti 1975</bibRefCitation>
: 251). It was first mentioned in 
<bibRefCitation author="Ferussac, AEJPJFd'Audebard de" journalOrPublisher="Poulet, Paris" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" publicationUrl="http://books.google.at/books?pg=PR5&amp;lpg=PA17&amp;id=NqpAAAAAcAAJ&amp;hl=de&amp;ots=x7ErJq1S5av=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false" refId="B142" refString="Ferussac, AEJPJFd'Audebard de, 1814. Memoires geologiques sur les terreins formes sous l'eau douce par les debris fossiles des mollusques vivant sur la terre ou dans l'eau non salee. Poulet, Paris, http://books.google.at/books?pg=PR5&amp;lpg=PA17&amp;id=NqpAAAAAcAAJ&amp;hl=de&amp;ots=x7ErJq1S5av=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false" title="Memoires geologiques sur les terreins formes sous l'eau douce par les debris fossiles des mollusques vivant sur la terre ou dans l'eau non salee." url="http://books.google.at/books?pg=PR5&amp;lpg=PA17&amp;id=NqpAAAAAcAAJ&amp;hl=de&amp;ots=x7ErJq1S5av=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false" year="1814">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
(1814)
</bibRefCitation>
as nomen nudum for a specimen from the Euphrates River. Later, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ferussac, AEJPJFd'Audebard de" journalOrPublisher="Memoires de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de Paris" pageId="308" pageNumber="309" pagination="132 - 164" publicationUrl="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/23445page/148/mode/1up" refId="B144" refString="Ferussac, AEJPJFd'Audebard de, 1823. Monographie des especes vivantes et fossiles du genre melanopside, Melanopsis, et observations geologiques a leur sujet. Memoires de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de Paris 1 (1): 132 - 164, http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/23445page/148/mode/1up" title="Monographie des especes vivantes et fossiles du genre melanopside, Melanopsis, et observations geologiques a leur sujet." url="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/23445page/148/mode/1up" volume="1" year="1823">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
(1823)
</bibRefCitation>
listed the name in synonymy of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ferussac" authorityYear="1822" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis nodosa" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="nodosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Melanopsis nodosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
, 1822. Unlike 
<bibRefCitation author="Pallary, P" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de l'Afrique du Nord" pageId="323" pageNumber="324" pagination="70 - 87" publicationUrl="http://bibdigital.rjb.csic.es/spa/Libro.php?Libro=1840" refId="B378" refString="Pallary, P, 1916. Observations relatives a la nomenclature des Melanopsis fossiles. Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de l'Afrique du Nord 7 (3): 70 - 87, http://bibdigital.rjb.csic.es/spa/Libro.php?Libro=1840" title="Observations relatives a la nomenclature des Melanopsis fossiles." url="http://bibdigital.rjb.csic.es/spa/Libro.php?Libro=1840" volume="7" year="1916">Pallary (1916)</bibRefCitation>
claimed and followed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Wenz, W" journalOrPublisher="Gastropoda extramarina tertiaria" pageId="333" pageNumber="334" pagination="2503 - 2886" refId="B542" refString="Wenz, W, 1929. Fossilium Catalogus I: Animalia. Gastropoda extramarina tertiaria vol. IX: 2503 - 2886" title="Fossilium Catalogus I: Animalia." volume="vol. IX" year="1929">Wenz (1929)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pallary" authorityYear="1916" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="affinis" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="affinis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">affinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is not to be preferred over 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ferussac" authorityYear="1822" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="nodosa" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="nodosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">nodosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, because at that time 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pallary" authorityYear="1916" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="affinis" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="affinis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">affinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was not an available name - it has never been described, indicated or illustrated (as, for example, wrongly presumed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Esu, D" journalOrPublisher="Geologica Romana" pageId="307" pageNumber="308" pagination="203 - 294" publicationUrl="http://www.dst.uniroma1.it/geologicaromana/Volumi/VOL%2013/GR_13_203_293_Esu%20et%20al.pdf" refId="B136" refString="Esu, D, Girotti, O, 1975. La malacofauna continentale del Plio-Pleistocene dell'Italia centrale. I. Paleontologia. Geologica Romana 13: 203 - 294, http://www.dst.uniroma1.it/geologicaromana/Volumi/VOL%2013/GR_13_203_293_Esu%20et%20al.pdf" title="La malacofauna continentale del Plio-Pleistocene dell'Italia centrale. I. Paleontologia." url="http://www.dst.uniroma1.it/geologicaromana/Volumi/VOL%2013/GR_13_203_293_Esu%20et%20al.pdf" volume="13" year="1975">Esu and Girotti 1975</bibRefCitation>
) and so does not fulfill the requirements of availability (Art. 11 and 12; see also Art. 11.6). 
<bibRefCitation author="Pallary, P" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de l'Afrique du Nord" pageId="323" pageNumber="324" pagination="70 - 87" publicationUrl="http://bibdigital.rjb.csic.es/spa/Libro.php?Libro=1840" refId="B378" refString="Pallary, P, 1916. Observations relatives a la nomenclature des Melanopsis fossiles. Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de l'Afrique du Nord 7 (3): 70 - 87, http://bibdigital.rjb.csic.es/spa/Libro.php?Libro=1840" title="Observations relatives a la nomenclature des Melanopsis fossiles." url="http://bibdigital.rjb.csic.es/spa/Libro.php?Libro=1840" volume="7" year="1916">Pallary (1916)</bibRefCitation>
was the first to affiliate the name with an illustration, namely the one of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ferussac" authorityYear="1822" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis nodosa" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="nodosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Melanopsis nodosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
provided by 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
, 1823 (pl. 7, fig. 13), and made the name thereby available. The illustrated specimen is, however, the holotype (by monotypy) of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ferussac" authorityYear="1822" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis nodosa" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="nodosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Melanopsis nodosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
, 1822 (
<normalizedToken originalValue="Férussac">Ferussac</normalizedToken>
used the same plates in both of his works and thus Pallary actually referred to the specimen illustrated as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ferussac" authorityYear="1822" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis nodosa" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="nodosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Melanopsis nodosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the &quot;Histoire naturelle&quot;; see also introduction and Table 
<tableCitation captionStart="Table 1" captionStartId="T1" captionText="Table 1. Ferussac's original figure legends of the two plates of &quot; Melanopsides fossiles &quot; (1822 / 1823) in the &quot; Histoire naturelle &quot;, compared with the altered legends supplied by Deshayes in 1839 when finalizing the work. Note that Ferussac's original figure legends for plate 1 are unavailable to me and thus based on the legends for plate 7 in Ferussac (1823), which are supposed to be identical (see text for details)." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/3E6FCC01983F825DC2CEDBCDC3712B51" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" tableUuid="3E6FCC01983F825DC2CEDBCDC3712B51">1</tableCitation>
for details of 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Férussac’s">Ferussac's</normalizedToken>
publications). Consequently, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pallary" authorityYear="1916" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis affinis" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="affinis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Melanopsis affinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Pallary, 1916 is a junior objective synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ferussac" authorityYear="1822" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis nodosa" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="nodosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Melanopsis nodosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Moreover, the name is a junior homonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pallary" authorityYear="1916" class="Gastropoda" family="Melanopsidae" genus="Melanopsis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Melanopsis affinis" order="Pteropoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="affinis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Melanopsis affinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Handmann, 1882.
</paragraph>
